    "description": "Grow your career with Cashfree Asia Pacific Associates! We are hiring a Credit Analyst for our Hyderabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Cashfree Asia Pacific Associates:\nCashfree Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cashfree Asia Pacific Associates!",
